/********************************************************************************
 * ~Exception();
 * 	Purpose: 
 * 		Destructor for Exception class
 * 		(just de-allocates the memory for the error message)
 * 	
 * 	Entry: 
 * 		A still allocated exception (this)
 * 	
 * 	Exit: 
 * 		A not allocated exception (that)
 * 	
 ********************************************************************************/
